Package model.area

Class Board

java.lang.Object
model.area.Board
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Board extends Object implements Serializable
This class represents the board with all the areas you can find in the physical board. In its different areas you can place the family members and also it contains the cards and the excommunication tiles.
